<div style="margin: -1em 0 1em; font-weight: 85%;">
<p><a href="/goc-hub-page">Global Occult Coalition Casefiles</a> » <a href="/goc-supplemental-threat-entities">PHYSICS Division Threat Entity Database</a> » UTE-1919-Discofather<br />
<a href="/groups-of-interest">Groups Of Interest</a> » <a href="/chicago-spirit">Chicago Spirit</a> » <a href="/black-as-night">Black As Night Hub</a> » UTE-1919-Discofather</p>
